
example:

create or edit best-practices/SKILL.md

$ zip -r best-practices.skill best-practices
$ mv best-practices.skill ~/Desktop

In Claude Desktop:

Options -> Capabilities -> Skills -> Add... best-practices.skill

(i.e. don't keep .skill files)

