typical novel 70-120,000 words

Claude is about 200,000 words - so about 2 novels worth of context.

Coot XML Doc is 10Mb, remove decoration that about 1.5 millon tokens

A factor of 7 or 8 times too much.

Documentation for AI has to be thematically separated.
Non-trivial


